title: Private Transfer Lima Airport (QuickLlama Airport Shuttle)
description: Prebook this Jorge Chavez International Airport Private Transfer from Lima and avoid the stress that comes with finding a last-minute ride to the airport for a private group. This transfer service tracks your flight at the LIM Airport to make sure you arrive on time for your departure flight. Plus, your comfortable van is equipped with air conditioning and Wi-Fi.
all_descriptions: Prebook this Jorge Chavez International Airport Private Transfer from Lima and avoid the stress that comes with finding a last-minute ride to the airport for a private group. This transfer service tracks your flight at the LIM Airport to make sure you arrive on time for your departure flight. Plus, your comfortable van is equipped with air conditioning and Wi-Fi.

• Our driver will arrive at the agreed pickup time to your hotel or address 
 • If you provided a phone number when booking, the driver will also WhatsApp you 5 minutes before arriving to let you know he is on his way 
 • Free WiFi onboard 
 • Air conditioning 
 • Security cameras 
 • GPS tracking 
 • Professional drivers 
 • Passengers are automatically covered by a private insurance policy that includes US$ 4,000 per person for medical expenses, US$20,000 per person for permanent disabilities and US$20,000 per person for fatalities 
 • Authorized to transport passengers nationwide by Peru's Ministry of Transportation and Communications 

Duration: The transfer to Lima Airport takes 1 hour on average (45 minutes when there is little traffic, 90 minutes with intense traffic) and also depends on where exactly you are staying. As a guidance: 
 • Lowest traffic is from 9 PM to 7 AM everyday - 45 minutes transfer time 
 • Highest traffic is from 7 AM to 9 AM and from 5 PM to 9 PM only on weekdays (Monday - Friday) - 90 minutes transfer time 
 • Moderate traffic from 9 AM to 5 PM on weekdays, and all day on weekends - 1 hour transfer time 

Pick up time suggestion: 
 • If you have a DOMESTIC flight, we suggest you to arrive at the airport between 1.5-2 hours before your flight 
 • If you have an INTERNATIONAL flight, we suggest you to arrive at the airport between 2-3 hours before your flight

reviews.title: ALTERNATIVA BUENA Y ECONÓMICA
reviews.text: La mejor alternativa para ir de Lima al aeropuerto. Muy cumplidos, serios y económicos. Mientras un taxi te puede costar 50 soles, ellos te llevan por 16. Los puntos de embarque son estratégicos y muy bien ubicados.REcomendado para quienes viajan solos.

reviews.title: Puntualidad
reviews.text: Confortables vehículos, puntuales.Lo malo: poco aire acondicionado, sin cinturones de seguridad para todos los asientos y hay que tomarlo fuera del aeropuerto
